  m_Text: This shows you how to draw a trail underneath all fingers touching the
    screen, and have them smoothly fade out over time when released. This is done
    using the <color=#0FF>LeanDragTrail</color> component, and you can control the
    visual style from the <color=#0FF>LineRenderer</color> prefab. Keep in mind this
    feature requires the <color=#0FF>LeanTouch.RecordFingers</color> setting to be
    enabled (it is by default).
